<br>
Keeping silent and patient,he watched as the Pegasus cautiously looked about,as if the winged beast could sence Bellerophons pressence,but uncaring,the Pegasus clomped over to the well,but once again it causiously looked about before kneeling to drink.<br>
<br>
Bellerophon sat in wait still grasping the golden bridal,until he knew the Pegasus was vulnerable,and just as that moment came,Bellerophon lept from his hiding spot,and with a few quick strides,and a leap he pounces on Pegasus.... <p>-=¤ Bellerophon ¤=-</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#336699><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/umobellerophon.showPublicProfile?language=EN>MO Bellerophon</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=IMG SRC="http://www.helicon.i-p.com/bellerophon-010.jpg" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 22<br> <font color=#FFFF33>(8/19/01 12:37 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=141.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://hometown.aol.com/alteredsoulsx/images/bellerophon-05.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> The struggle</span><hr size=1> Pegasus barely had time to react as Bellerophon jumped on him,but the winged beast was not yet going to give in,and just before Bellerophon could slip the bridle on,the Pegasus kicked and lept into the air,flapping those large wings of his,Pegasus tried desperatly to rid himself of Bellerophon.<br>
<br>
But Bellerophon was a great tamer of horses,and was more than up to such a challenge.He held onto Pegasus,his left arm firmly wrapped around the creatures neck,as he continued to clentch the golden bridle in his right hand.<br>
<br>
Just as Bellerophon brought his right hand up to desperatly try to slip the bridle over Pegasus' head,the beast flew higher bucking,trying to shake Bellerophon off.Bellerophon losing some of his grip,slips from Pegasus' back,but clings tightly to Pegasus' white mane.He dangled there for a moment while Pegasus continues to try and shake him,but to no avail.With all his might,Bellerophon pulls himself back onto Pegasus' back.Tightly he clings to the animal with his legs,his left hand still holding onto the mane,and with some effort he finally slips the bridle onto Pegasus' head,and tightens.<br>
<br>
Though the bridle was now firmly attached,Pegasus continued to try to shake Bellerophon,but to no avail.Bellerophon gives a nice hard tug on the bridle,showing that he had won the struggle.And now Pegasus knew,he had a new master. <p>-=¤ Bellerophon ¤=-</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#003366><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/umobellerophon.showPublicProfile?language=EN>MO Bellerophon</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=IMG SRC="http://www.helicon.i-p.com/bellerophon-010.jpg" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 23<br> <font color=#FFFF33>(8/19/01 12:45 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=141.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://hometown.aol.com/alteredsoulsx/images/bellerophon-05.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> The first battle won...</span><hr size=1> Once realized the Pegasus was now under the control of Bellerophon,Bellerophon goes for a little flight,but not a long one,for he has another mission to accomplish,and soon after,he leads the Pegasus to his black steed,where he dismounts Pegasus,and ties off the reigns to a tree.<br>
<br>
